headline: Accenture to Acquire Soben, Boosting Capital Projects Capabilities in Data Center Development and Other Sectors
summary: GLASGOW, Scotland, March 11, 2025--Accenture has agreed to acquire Soben, a global provider of construction consultancy services, headquartered in Glasgow, Scotland.
